BTW, here's my own view on religion and faith, but I suspect it will offend a lot of people.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I view faith as an abdication of intellect and a worshiping of ignorance.  It is the greatest evil on the face of the earth (yes, I am serious about that).  It breeds intolerance, hate, bigotry, etc. etc..  All of those are identical to religion in that they elevate belief beyond the realm of a simple hope into the realm of fact.  The very definition of faith hinges on accepting as fact something that you do not know is true or not and for which there is even negative evidence.  God is Santa Claus for moral imbecilles.<br>
<br>
Oh, yes, I have a faith myself: I believe that someday the human race will grow up.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usyllestraefv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Syllestrae FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderating inconsistently<br>since Jun 2002</span><br>  Posts: 1426<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/2/02 1:31:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=745.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: I think you just opened a can of worms ..</span><hr size=1> It can stay here for now.  If things get out of hand it'll most likely just get locked, not moved to soapbox.  /squints at everyone <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
